Be a catalyst for better.
Explore careers at The Chemours Company, from chemical engineering to business management.
Search Jobs








A career at Chemours helps shape the future of chemistry. 
Chemours is a new company, with products and processes that enable many of the basics of modern life. We are formulating ways to make ordinary things extraordinary.
 
Chemours is a $6 billion startup with global scale. We collaborate with customers to make cars cooler, homes warmer, food fresher, colors bolder. We use chemistry to change lives, shape markets, and redefine industries, and we do it one improvement at a time.
Here, you can help create a more colorful, capable, and cleaner world through the power of chemistry. 



Making Ordinary Things Extraordinary
At Chemours, you can work on lower global warming potential (GWP) refrigerants for air conditioners and refrigerators in our Fluoroproducts business. On pigments that raise hiding power, so less paint covers more, in our Titanium Technologies business. On biosecurity products that help safeguard farms and food with our Chemical Solutions.
Practicing Collective Entrepreneurship
Working at a new company, you will have a chance to contribute to evolving our business, our chemistry, and our culture. The "ours" in Chemours is for all of us who work here. We're thousands strong and looking for new people to help make us stronger and who want to grow with us.  
 




   
						



Chemours employees live chemistry, every day, because it’s more than a job—it’s a passion. Living Chemistry empowers our team to be catalysts for change, and helps our customers do better, be better, and build better. 
				


 
 






