CODE OF CONDUCT
The Chemours Code of Conduct is designed to guide employees through our values and ethical standards in day-to-day business interactions. At Chemours one of our values is Unshakable Integrity and our Code of Conduct is the foundation for bringing that value to life in our organization.
View Code of Conduct






















