Titanium Technologies 


Titanium Technologies is the Global Source for TiO2
Titanium Technologies 
The world's largest producer of titanium dioxide, making Ti-Pure™ products for coatings, plastics, laminates, and paper.
Learn More
Learn More >














Fluoroproducts


The World's Largest Maker of Fluoropolymers and Fluorochemicals
Fluoroproducts
A leading maker of fluoroproducts, including Teflon™ fluoropolymers, Viton™ fluoroelastomers, Krytox™ lubricants, and Opteon™ refrigerants.
Learn More
Learn More >














Chemical Solutions


Chemical Solutions for Challenging Processes
Chemical Solutions
Chemours is a leader in the safe and efficient production of high-quality industrial chemical products, including sodium cyanide for mining, Glypure™ glycolic acid, Vazo™ chemical initiators, methylamine, and aniline.
Learn More
Learn More >





















