Ethics Hotline 


Ethics Hotline 
The The Chemours Ethics Hotline is a multi-lingual service to ask a question or to report a suspected violation of the Chemours Code of Conduct. This service is available 24 hours a day, 7 days a week.  All reports are treated with the appropriate confidentiality and where it is legally allowed you may also choose to remain anonymous.
Contact Hotline
